{"tid":1438020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［關心前線警員］全民請阿Sir飲汽水大行動！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-09T16:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:54:53.000Z","uid":23707,"like":60,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"012e8b81dcb4d67e21d73c6a9b174d11bf023944","tid":1438020,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:20:03.000Z","msg":"炎炎夏日 阿Sir full gear一定好辛苦<br />\n我正式呼籲大家聽日一齊請阿Sir飲汽水！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過聽講啲阿Sir好怕一種叫做不明液體嘅液體<br />\n所以我建議大家請阿Sir飲芬達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就係人都知係咩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然 有人唔鐘意飲汽水<br />\n各類飲品都可以請阿Sir飲<br />\n甜嘢當然為主啦<br />\n可以幫前線警員補充體力啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7KteBBi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7KteBBi.png&h=1f3cbbc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hnk4YOi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhnk4YOi.png&h=294fd16b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zWKYiOj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzWKYiOj.png&h=4b724b71&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BPEENGF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBPEENGF.png&h=5bd35f11&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zo45Je1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZo45Je1.png&h=6c8548ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ngApemH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FngApemH.png&h=299b639a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"ht